    "Considering the streamwise and crosswise velocity components defined as U(x, t) and V(x, t), respectively, being x = (x, y) with x and y the streamwise and crosswise coordinates and t the time.",
    "We decompose the velocity components as:",
    "Uðx,tÞ = UðxÞ + uðx,tÞ, V ðx,tÞ = V ðxÞ + vðx,tÞ",
    "where UðxÞ and V ðxÞ are the streamwise and crosswise time-averaged velocity components and u(x, t) and v(x, t) are the streamwise and crosswise fluctuating velocity components.",
